*<> - Compulsory, [] - Optional
Commands:
/permban <player> [reason] - Permenantly bans a player
/tempban <player> [time(s/m/h/d)] [reason] - Temporarily bans a player (Defaults to 15 minutes) (Must provide time for ban reason)
/unban <player> [reason] - Unbans a player
/mute <player> [reason] - Mutes a player permenantly
/tempmute <player> [time(s/m/h/d)] [reason] - Temporarily Mutes a player for specific time
/unmute <player> [reason]	-	Unmutes a Player
/bc reload - Reloads Plugin
/shutup [time] - Mute/Unmute chat (defaults 15 minutes)